      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.SRkvq0GXYm3Wi6ze]{Spellbrawler}</p>\n<p>By either spending 1 Resolve Point or dismissing the AC bonus granted by your @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.QopuFVX0mdGrmpSy]{Spell Siphon} as a move action, you empower your next successful attack made against a target within 30 feet before the end of your next turn to disrupt magic. This functions as @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.KQ4vSfG9tq8EJxir]{Dispel Magic} for the targeted dispel function, using your soldier level as the dispel check’s caster level. At 17th level, this can instead function as @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.1FfFraWlxCu1L4rL]{Dispel Magic, Greater} for the targeted dispel function. Once you use this ability, you can’t use it again until you have regained Stamina Points following a 10-minute rest.</p>"
